h1.font: Step6a: Multivalued attributes A of Entity E1 require a composite PK of (E1.PKFK1, E1.A)

div.p: If an entity E1 has a multivalued attribute A and primary key E1.PK, the corresponding relation R must have a composite PK made of (E1.PKFK1, E1.A) where E1.PKFK1 is a foreign key to E1.PK.
